an|Marasigan]] {{goal|50}}\n[[Bienvenido Mara\u00f1\u00f3n|Mara\u00f1\u00f3n]] {{goal|81||87}}\n|team2=[[Green Archers United F.C.|Green Archers United]]\n|goals2=[[John Celiz|Celiz]] {{goal|24}}\n|stadium=[[Aboitiz Pitch, Lipa|Aboitiz Pitch]]\n|location=[[Lipa, Batangas|Lipa]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=W}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|id=\n|date={{Start date|2019|10|14}}\n|time=19:00 [[Philippine Standard Time|UTC+8]]\n|round=23\n|score=3\u20130\n|report=\n|team1=Ceres\u2013Negros\n|goals1=[[Takashi Odawara|Odawara]] {{goal|2}}<br>[[Bienvenido Mara\u00f1\u00f3n|Mara\u00f1\u00f3n]] {{goal|35||74}}\n|team2=[[Mendiola F.C. 1991|Mendiola]]\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Aboitiz Pitch, Lipa|Aboitiz Pitch]]\n|location=[[Lipa, Batangas|Lipa]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=W}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|id=\n|date={{Start date|2019|10|19}}\n|time=16:00 [[Philippine Standard Time|UTC+8]]\n|round=24\n|score=0\u20133\n|report=\n|team1=[[Kaya F.C.|Kaya\u2013Iloilo]]\n|goals1=\n|team2=Ceres\u2013Negros\n|goals2=[[OJ Porteria|Porteria]] {{goal|73}}<br>[[Bienvenido Mara\u00f1\u00f3n|Mara\u00f1\u00f3n]] {{goal|90}}<br>[[James Younghusband|Younghusband]] {{goal|90+3}}\n|stadium=[[Aboitiz Pitch, Lipa|Aboitiz Pitch]]\n|location=[[Lipa, Batangas|Lipa]]\n|attendance=\n|referee=\n|result=W}}\nNote:\n: '''a''' {{note|a1}}Global forfeited the match due to an inability to field a team. The result was 0-3 in favor of Ceres.\n\n=== Copa Paulino Alcantara ===\n{{main|2019 Copa Paulino Alcantara}}\n\n==== Group Stage ====\nOn October 20, Ceres\u2013Negros were drawn in '''Group A''' of the [[Copa Paulino Alcantara]] alongside [[Mendiola F.C. 1991|Mendiola]], [[Green Archers United F.C.|Green Archers United]], and [[Philippines national under-23 football team|Philippines U22]].<ref>{{cite news |last1=Terrado |first1=Jonas |title=SEAG squad drawn with Ceres in Copa Paulino Alcantara |url=https://sports.mb.com.ph/2019/10/21/seag-squad-drawn-with-ceres-in-copa-paulino-alcantara/ |accessdate